               <msContents>
                  <summary/> 
            
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <title type="complete" xml:lang="gez" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1019Actsof">መጽሐፈ፡ ግብረ፡ ልዑካን፡ ዝንቱ፡ ውእቱ፡ ዜና፡
                ሐዋርያት፡ ንጹሓን፡ እምጊዜ፡ ዕርገቱ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ዘጸሐፈ፡ ሉቃስ፡ ጠቢብ፡ ወንጌላዊ፡
              ወፈነዎ፡ ኀበ፡ ታኦፊላ፡ ዘጸሐፈ፡ ሎቱ፡ ቀዳሚ፡ ወንግለ።</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     <note>The chapters are irregularly marked and not numbered.</note>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">እስከዝ፡ ነገር፡ አብጽሐ፡ ሉቃስ፡ በዜናሁ። ወእምዝ፡ ተስወረ፡ እምኔሁ፡
              እስመ፡ አንተ፡ ትረክብ፡ በቀዳሚ፡ ፍካሬ፡ መልእክተ፡ ጳውሎስ፡ ዜና፡ ግብረ፡ ጳውሎስ። እስመ፡ ውእቱ፡ ቦአ፡
              ኀበ፡ ኔሮን፡ በቀዳማይ፡ ጊዜ፡ ሞአ፡ ወሖረ፡ በሰላም። ወእምድኅረዝ፡ ነበረ፡ ኑኀ፡ ፪ዓመታተ፡ 
              ወወጽአ። ወእምዝ፡ ተመይጠ፡ ወአጥመቀ፡ አዝማዲሁ፡
              ለኔሮን፡ ወስምዓ፡ ኮነ፡ በአዴሁ፡ በሰይፍ፡ ዕጉሠ።</explicit>
                     
                     <note>The text generally agrees with that of <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/CJRDF5NJ"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Platt1830novum"/><title level="m">Novum testamentum domini nostri et servatoris Jesu Christi aethiopice</title><editor><forename>Thomas Pell</forename><surname>Platt</surname></editor><pubPlace>Londini</pubPlace><publisher>Impressit Ricardus Watts</publisher><date>1830</date><note type="url">https://archive.org/details/novumtestamentu00platgoog</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Manuscripts</note><note type="tag">New Testament</note><note type="tag">bm:Platt1830novum</note></note><note type="tag">Manuscripts</note><note type="tag">New Testament</note><note type="tag">bm:Platt1830novum</note></bibl>,  which represents the revised version.</note>
                  </msItem>
              
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="49r">Fols 49r and following</locus>
                     <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3179Revela">Revelation of
                                                  John</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
              
            
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.1">
                        <locus from="49r">Fols 49r and following</locus>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3179Revela#Revelation">Revelation of John, Revelation</title>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">ዘዮሐንስ፡ ኢጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ዘቍስጥንጥንያ፡
                መጥሮጶሊስ፡ አመ፡ ሀለዎ፡ ይስደድ፡ ራዕዩ፡ ለዮሐንስ፡ ዘከመ፡ ርእዮ፡ ለኢየሱስ፡ ዘወሀቦ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ከመ፡
                ያርእዮሙ፡ ለአግብርቲሁ፡ ዘሀለዎ፡ ይኩን፡ ፍጡነ።</incipit>
                        <note>For the first sentence, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘዮሐንስ፡ ኢጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ዘቍስጥንጥንያ፡
                  መጥሮጶሊስ፡ አመ፡ ሀለዎ፡ ይስደድ፡</foreign>, see also:
                <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/NMHJ56PR"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Dillmann1848Catalogus"/><title level="m">Catalogus codicum manuscriptorum Bibliothecae Bodleianae Oxoniensis, Pars VII: Codices Aethiopici</title><author><forename>Christian Friedrich August</forename><surname>Dillmann</surname></author><pubPlace>Oxonii</pubPlace><publisher>E Typographeo Academico</publisher><date>1848</date><note type="url">https://archive.org/details/CatalogiCodicumManuscriptorumBibliothP7</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Oxford</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">bm:Dillmann1848Catalogus</note></note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Oxford</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">bm:Dillmann1848Catalogus</note><citedRange unit="page">19</citedRange></bibl>
                        </note>
                        <explicit xml:lang="gez">በዝየ፡ ተፈጸመ፡ ራእየ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ አቡቀለምሲስ፡ ዝውእቱ፡ ብሂል፡ ዘርእየ፡ በሕይወቱ፡ 
                  ራእየ፡ መንክራተ።</explicit>
                        <note>The beginnings of the following passages are rubricated and indicate the book's divisions:
                  <p>1:1</p>
                           <p>2:1; 2:7; 2:11; 2:29b</p>
                           <p>3:6b; 3:13b; 3:22b</p>
                           <p>4:10b</p>
                           <p>5:5; 5:9; 5:14</p>
                           <p>6:1; 6:3; 6:5; 6:7; 6:9; 6:12</p>
                           <p>7:13</p>
                           <p>8:1; 8:7; 8:8; 8:10; 8:12</p>
                           <p>9:1; 9:13</p>
                           <p>11:15</p>
                           <p>12:10</p>
                           <p>13:10</p>
                           <p>14:6; 14:8; 14:9; 14:13</p>
                           <p>15:3</p>
                           <p>16:7; 16:17</p>
                           <p>18:1</p>
                        </note>
                        <note>The text generally agrees with that of <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/CJRDF5NJ"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Platt1830novum"/><title level="m">Novum testamentum domini nostri et servatoris Jesu Christi aethiopice</title><editor><forename>Thomas Pell</forename><surname>Platt</surname></editor><pubPlace>Londini</pubPlace><publisher>Impressit Ricardus Watts</publisher><date>1830</date><note type="url">https://archive.org/details/novumtestamentu00platgoog</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Manuscripts</note><note type="tag">New Testament</note><note type="tag">bm:Platt1830novum</note></note><note type="tag">Manuscripts</note><note type="tag">New Testament</note><note type="tag">bm:Platt1830novum</note></bibl>, except for a certain number of variants. </note>
                     </msItem>
              
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.2">
                        <locus from="74r">Fols 74r and following</locus> 
                        
                        <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3179Revela#Introduction">Revelation of John, Introduction to
                                                  Revelation</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">ምክንያተ፡ ጽሕፈቱሰ፡ ለአብያተ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ዘጸሐፈ፡ ለሰብዑ፡ አብያተ፡ ክርስቲያናት፡ ኮነ፡ 
                  በእንተ፡ ፫ግብር፡ ፩በእንተ፡ ዘኀደጉ፡ ግብረ፡ ዘመሀሮሙ፡ ቀዳሚ፡ ወካልእ፡ በእንተ፡ ዘይከውን፡ እምጥንተ፡ ዘርእየ፡ እስከ፡
                  ምጽአቱ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ወሣልስ፡ ሥርዓተ፡ መልእክቱ፡ ዘርእየ፡ ከመ፡ ያርኢ፡ ለቀሳውስት፡ ወለዲያቆናት።</incipit>
                     </msItem>
                  </msItem>
            
